---
layout: base.liquid
---
<main class="md-layout">
  <aside class="md-sidebar">
    <div class="md-tabs">
      <button id="tab-v1" class="md-tab md-tab-active">v1</button>
      <button id="tab-v2" class="md-tab">v2</button>
    </div>
    <div class="md-controls">
      <button id="play-pause" class="md-play-pause" aria-label="Play/Pause">
        <svg id="icon-play" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><polygon points="5,3 19,12 5,21"/></svg>
        <svg id="icon-pause" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" style="display:none"><rect x="5" y="3" width="4" height="18"/><rect x="15" y="3" width="4" height="18"/></svg>
      </button>
      <span class="font-mono md-gen">generation <span id="generation">0</span>/<span id="max-generation">0</span></span>
    </div>
    <input type="range" id="scrubber" min="0" max="0" value="0">
    <div id="image-selector"></div>
    <p id="desc-v1" class="md-desc">one game of life. light pixels are alive, dark pixels are dead. all four colors share a single simulation.</p>
    <p id="desc-v2" class="md-desc" style="display:none">four independent games of life, one per color. dead cells are transparent. lightest color layered on top, darkest on bottom.</p>
  </aside>
  <div class="md-canvas-wrap">
    <canvas id="machinic-canvas"></canvas>
  </div>
</main>
